| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-5663 — Recovery Inhibition (medusa)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 747c1eed-e9f0-5e5b-a3d3-2edc8bf16c60"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
